Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:05.35,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}禁锢着开启心灵的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:10.00,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}你是开启这锁的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:15.50,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}只愿你能拯救那笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.98,0:01:21.13,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夏风的指引  带来变革的风暴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:25.82,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}将波长同步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:31.28,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如同浪漫故事般  善解人意的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:33.84,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}也无处可寻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.18,0:01:40.38,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}只能以蓝天为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.59,0:01:45.22,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如此我们就能合而为一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:50.58,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}无论是迷茫的泪水  还是梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:57.02,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}都是能被真实所吸引之物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:02:00.88,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}那即是太过惹人怜爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:05.43,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}魔法的记忆
