Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:56.42,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}但你总是目不转睛地注视着明天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:22:02.20,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}究竟要付出多少泪水为代价？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:09.02,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}所以你也能将我们的迷惘化作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.46,0:22:15.50,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}解放紧密相连的心灵——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:21.95,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Believe  这份满溢而出的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.24,0:22:28.60,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}In the dreaming  只为某人而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.12,0:22:34.50,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}凭借这份微小的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.32,0:22:40.16,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不管风会有多么猛烈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:47.72,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我都想要守护你
